              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/44962552/" class="">第179页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/158011371/" class=" " title="木小嘉">木小嘉</a>
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="44962552">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">官场人和事都复杂，没有深入了解，看到的听到的或许都是假象。</span>
                <p class="pl">
